678
00:39:00,750 --> 00:39:01,999
Mas Shri Rama disse:

679
00:39:02,000 --> 00:39:04,917
"Eu nunca comi frutas tão maravilhosas."

680
00:39:05,125 --> 00:39:08,125
"Elas são as frutas mais maravilhosas que Eu comi."

681
00:39:08,375 --> 00:39:09,667
